<subSubSection pageId="37" pageNumber="521" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="37.[1381,2587,283,433]" pageId="37" pageNumber="521">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1382,1729,283,312]" pageId="37" pageNumber="521">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Broadtoothed Tailless Bat seems locally common in its large distribution.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
